title: Are Your Getting Brainwashed?
itunes:title: Are Your Getting Brainwashed?
description:
Episode 590 - We are all getting brainwashed by something, whether we realize it or not, and there are studies to prove it! The good thing is that we are in control of our brainwashing if we decide to take control of it. Listen to this episode to learn how to stop being brainwashed and start brainwashing yourself!
